survey_response.review_text:
Very very Good and I suggest and recommend to everyone .
Explain the issue very well and good.                        .        ...........

Dr.Lakshmi is a wonderful person, she treated my 70 year and 60 year mother with with utmost care. She gave complete flexibility for the subsequent visits. Her respect and ability to treat the person with patience is amazing. She made the entire procedure absolutely painfree. I highly recommend this doctor for any dental treatment. Thank you doctor for the care and concern you showed towards my parents. You made them feel very comfortable for the treatment and they have complete confidence and trust in you.

First of all it is located in a hard to find place. Secondly even after asking for directions twice, nobody guided us to this dental clinic properly ..we asked the person coordinating the appointment s and he gave wrong directions. It's a pain to reach that spot because of dirty and bad roads around it. Dentist was alright but clinic is dirty. No proper hygiene is maintained. Overall, it's average. Many other good dental centres and dentists are available in Bangalore. I don't think I will take my kid again there because it's poorly maintained and zero hygiene.

** *** *** ******* *** * ************* *** ***** **** ** *** ** **** *******I had taken my 7 year old kid for the treatment for cavities.She said there is a puss collection in the roots, *** *** *** *** ****** *** **** *** filled it with the temporary filling. the gums started swelling up and the puss started coming out from the gums. I took her again  to the doctor, she said it is not related to the filling.

We revisited as we liked Dr. Lakshmi's treatment and because the clinic used to charge reasonably. However during this visit, they seem to have increased the rates irrationally. A simple teeth filing for which we were charged Rs. 500 earlier was charged Rs. 800 this time, which is exceptionally high *** **** ****** ********** This was brought to notice of clinic supervisor but they still charged the same. Not sure if we will visit 32 smiles again. Maybe they can take this as a feedback and start charging reasonably in order to retain their customers.

I went for my son's tooth extraction the doctor was very polite and friendly and my son didn't cry at all it was a Great experience I would recommend anyone for any dental issues to do visit the doctor Also it is a very neat and clean premise thank you for the help the doctor

We went to Dr.Lakshmi for my daughter's teeth concern, initially we planned to do 4 RCT but later after checking Dr.Lakshmi suggested root canal is only required for 2 teeth. She is very experienced, ******** * ****** ******* ******* does the treatment only for what is required. Treatment is **** ***** comfortable and we are satisfied. Thanks to Dr.Lakshmi.

I booked the doctor thru Practo and got confirmation to visit. I had to travel 1 hour to reach the clinic and I took the confirmation can be trustable.
When I reached there, they took my baby for consultation, they started diagnose, they didn't even ask anything. Finally they came and told that Doctor will visit after 4 days and she will fix the teeth. 
They charged 100 rupees for telling this.
If they doctor is not there, why they accepted appointment?
Why they didn't show the courtesy to tell when I went there ?

Some other doctor looked the case instead of her. Clinic is not maintained properly. I went there for kids dentist but in vain 
Please avoid this doctor.

Good treatment.

*** ** * **** ******* explained very well the problems and the resolution. I would recommend the Doctor for dental issues

Visited for my sons puppectumy treatment. Doctor is very courteous and professional. She has explained in detail. She was ready to extended session if the kid is having problems or pain. Recommended this doctor for pediatric treatment.
Doctor is very much polite and described the issue patiently and clearly. Definitely I will recommend to visit her  for any kids dental problems.
She is very cool while doing the treatment. Coming on time to clinic and  proving the treatment in systematic manner.

The doctor was polite and explained to me with the procedure.
my son, who is of 7 years was comfortable with the doctor,and my son was happy to have his treatment done
The treatment was really good and it was completed in a short period of 20 minutes. Fee is very high.
She exactly knows the pulse of kids and can persuade them to cooperate. This is our second visit to doctor and we are very happy
